## Scope Touched
- `Contract.sol` â€” core Balancer `exitPool` callback / exit-path state-transition surface; repeated focus on whether transient LP state can be consumed before pricing, solvency, collateral-disable, withdrawal, or borrow checks settle
- `FlawVerifier.sol` â€” main exploit-reachability harness for inflated collateral valuation, health-factor decisions, collateral removal sequencing, and possible same-window borrow reachability
